Copy all module files to /etc/nixos/modules/
Copy qtile-autostart.sh to /etc/nixos/
Paste the configuration.nix to /etc/nixos/

Run:
sudo nixos-rebuild switch


This gives you a fully modular, clean setup:
Qtile + Picom + Rofi
Chrome + 1Password + AnyDesk
VLC + HEVC/HEIF/AV1 codecs
Thunar + SMB support
AMD GPU optimization
LightDM + printing + Bluetooth
User and fonts ready
